text: Philip Andrew Collins (born March 8, 1967) is an American politician. He is the Prohibition Party's presidential nominee for the 2020 presidential election. Collins was active in local politics in Illinois and Nevada. In 2019, he ran for Mayor of Las Vegas for the 2019 mayoral election where he came in second place. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Illinois Category:2020 United States presidential candidates Category:Politicians from Las Vegas
